Interface ISearchIterator

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Iterator<ISearchResultItem>

    public interface ISearchIterator
extends Iterator<ISearchResultItem>
    Represents an iterator for the convenient iteration of the search results

        Replaces the value of the current element by the given value or removes the element if it doesn't match the search conditions

        Parameters:
        replacement - the value for the replacement
        Throws:
        UnsupportedOperationException - if replace is not supported
